courses.learning_outcomes:
1. To have a good understanding of the historical development of the architectural style in Hong Kong through different period;
2. To be able to identify style of architectural elements of historical buidlings in Hong Kong ranging from Chinese traditional buildings to buildings with colonial influence;
3. To be able to reference the buildings style appear in Hong Kong to the larger context, such as Chinese Architectural developmentin souther China and the Colonial Architectural devlopment in Asia.
